#######################
#  Sample conditions  #
#######################

save_sample_conditions_1
   _Saveframe_category   sample_conditions

   _Details              .

   loop_
      _Variable_type
      _Variable_value
      _Variable_value_error
      _Variable_value_units

       temperature     273   . K   
       pH                6.8 . pH  
       pressure          1   . atm 
      'ionic strength'   0.1 . M   

   stop_

save_


